title: Baguette & Chocolat
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Take-out, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe in the city centre offering coffee and smoothies, pastries and lunch items such as sandwiches, soups, and salads. Ovo-lacto vegetarians will be able to find something to eat, but vegan only the lentil soup. Sandwiches contain egg and/or cheese. Has almond and soy milk for drinks.
